286
00:16:15,440 --> 00:16:16,920
We'll leave first. No.

287
00:16:16,960 --> 00:16:19,120
Too many things to do. Let's go.

288
00:16:19,640 --> 00:16:21,320
Next time my father comes to inspect,

289
00:16:21,320 --> 00:16:22,840
remember to come in early and give me a signal

290
00:16:22,840 --> 00:16:23,880
to help me get away.

291
00:16:23,880 --> 00:16:24,610
Understood.

292
00:16:25,680 --> 00:16:26,240
Please come in.

293
00:16:26,240 --> 00:16:27,120
Please come in.

294
00:16:27,160 --> 00:16:28,840
I missed you so much, sir.

295
00:16:30,240 --> 00:16:31,240
What are you afraid of?

296
00:16:31,240 --> 00:16:32,280
We are here to investigate a case,

297
00:16:32,280 --> 00:16:33,720
not to seek pleasure.

298
00:16:34,360 --> 00:16:35,800
Let's go.

299
00:16:36,040 --> 00:16:38,040
Don't go weak in the knees. Let's go. Come on.

300
00:16:38,040 --> 00:16:39,370
Please come in, you two.

301
00:16:39,840 --> 00:16:41,280
If I bring you to this kind of place,

302
00:16:41,280 --> 00:16:42,720
and Lord Li finds out,

303
00:16:42,800 --> 00:16:44,480
I'm afraid I'll lose my job.

304
00:16:45,120 --> 00:16:46,650
Don't be afraid. It's fine.

305
00:16:48,280 --> 00:16:49,740
Have you been here before?

306
00:16:49,760 --> 00:16:51,240
I never come here.

307
00:16:51,520 --> 00:16:52,920
Are these pastries good?

308
00:16:53,040 --> 00:16:55,370
Her osmanthus cakes are especially good.

309
00:17:01,040 --> 00:17:01,720
Boss.

310
00:17:01,760 --> 00:17:03,040
This is really boring.

311
00:17:03,120 --> 00:17:04,280
I'm not having any fun at all.

312
00:17:04,280 --> 00:17:05,680
Mr. Chen.

313
00:17:05,880 --> 00:17:07,480
Why are you not having fun?

314
00:17:08,119 --> 00:17:10,319
There's no curfew around the Ghost Festival.

315
00:17:10,319 --> 00:17:12,380
You must stay a little longer anyway.

316
00:17:12,520 --> 00:17:14,079
Chuntao.

317
00:17:14,160 --> 00:17:15,220
Come here quickly.

318
00:17:15,960 --> 00:17:17,520
Let me introduce some nice girls to you.

319
00:17:17,520 --> 00:17:18,319
Hurry!

320
00:17:18,359 --> 00:17:20,160
Give Master Chen a pot of good wine.

321
00:17:20,160 --> 00:17:21,359
Enjoy your drink.

322
00:17:21,400 --> 00:17:22,839
Have fun, Master Chen. Come on.

323
00:17:22,839 --> 00:17:24,440
What would you like to drink today, Master?

324
00:17:24,440 --> 00:17:25,599
I'll leave it to you.

325
00:17:26,480 --> 00:17:28,079
Dance with more passion.

326
00:17:28,119 --> 00:17:29,160
Smile!

327
00:17:29,960 --> 00:17:32,160
Don't act like the guests owe you money.

328
00:17:40,280 --> 00:17:41,840
Isn't this Constable Su?

329
00:17:42,080 --> 00:17:44,000
What brings you here?

330
00:17:44,360 --> 00:17:47,480
The wind of solving cases, of course.

331
00:17:47,680 --> 00:17:48,560
It's not convenient for me

332
00:17:48,560 --> 00:17:50,600
to come here without official business,

333
00:17:50,600 --> 00:17:51,160
right?

334
00:17:52,720 --> 00:17:53,280
Today,

335
00:17:55,240 --> 00:17:56,640
I'm here to find someone.

336
00:17:57,320 --> 00:17:58,650
Who are you looking for?

337
00:17:58,760 --> 00:18:00,840
There are no suspicious people here.

338
00:18:00,960 --> 00:18:02,920
Does Miss Wang Mingzhu live here?

339
00:18:05,520 --> 00:18:08,250
Are there clues about Wang Kang's cause of death?

340
00:18:08,960 --> 00:18:10,400
We are still investigating.

341
00:18:10,400 --> 00:18:13,800
There are some details of the case we need to ask her in person.

342
00:18:14,120 --> 00:18:14,840
Sure.

343
00:18:15,080 --> 00:18:16,800
I'll have someone take you to her.

344
00:18:16,800 --> 00:18:17,720
That's alright.

345
00:18:17,720 --> 00:18:18,760
I'll take her to the backyard.

346
00:18:18,760 --> 00:18:20,320
We can find her and ask ourselves.

347
00:18:20,320 --> 00:18:20,800
Alright.

348
00:18:20,800 --> 00:18:22,240
You go back to your work.

349
00:18:23,240 --> 00:18:25,370
You seem quite familiar with my place.

350
00:18:27,000 --> 00:18:27,930
Never been here.

351
00:18:28,320 --> 00:18:28,880
My lady,

352
00:18:28,960 --> 00:18:31,220
where is the backyard? This way, please.

353
00:18:31,920 --> 00:18:33,560
This is their backyard.

354
00:18:34,000 --> 00:18:35,600
They usually rehearse here,

355
00:18:35,800 --> 00:18:37,120
start fires,

356
00:18:37,160 --> 00:18:38,120
and cook here.

357
00:18:38,280 --> 00:18:40,040
No men are allowed to come here.

358
00:18:43,480 --> 00:18:45,080
It still feels fishy.

359
00:18:52,640 --> 00:18:53,640
Why are you here?

360
00:18:54,720 --> 00:18:55,760
I live here.

361
00:18:57,320 --> 00:18:59,400
You live here?

362
00:19:00,480 --> 00:19:01,800
You can live here?

363
00:19:02,200 --> 00:19:03,440
Is there a problem?

364
00:19:06,520 --> 00:19:09,320
Have you found the murderer who killed my brother?

365
00:19:11,040 --> 00:19:12,440
Let's sit down and talk.

366
00:19:16,240 --> 00:19:17,400
For now,

367
00:19:17,600 --> 00:19:19,060
we don't have any news yet.

368
00:19:19,280 --> 00:19:21,520
We came today mainly to ask you,

369
00:19:21,960 --> 00:19:24,560
how was the relationship between Wang Kang and Wanqing?

370
00:19:24,560 --> 00:19:27,760
Why did you two ask me the same question one after another?

371
00:19:27,920 --> 00:19:29,850
You also suspect Nanrong Wanqing?

372
00:19:34,120 --> 00:19:35,920
Today in the morgue,

373
00:19:36,160 --> 00:19:38,040
while examining Wang Kang's body,

374
00:19:38,040 --> 00:19:38,840
I found that

375
00:19:38,880 --> 00:19:42,160
his clothes had gold threads from a Jiaofang costume entangled on them.

376
00:19:42,160 --> 00:19:44,800
And there was gold powder under his nails.

377
00:19:45,760 --> 00:19:46,600
I suspect

378
00:19:46,640 --> 00:19:48,040
the last person he saw

379
00:19:48,080 --> 00:19:49,480
was Nanrong Wanqing.

380
00:19:50,520 --> 00:19:51,400
What about you?

381
00:19:51,920 --> 00:19:53,240
What's your basis?

382
00:19:54,920 --> 00:19:57,200
The deceased, Qi Nianyao, told me

383
00:19:57,520 --> 00:20:00,000
she was killed by Wanqing.

384
00:20:02,600 --> 00:20:03,280
You

385
00:20:04,160 --> 00:20:05,200
can see ghosts?

386
00:20:08,400 --> 00:20:11,530
Both the deceased Wang Kang and Qi Nianyao knew Wanqing.

387
00:20:12,200 --> 00:20:14,920
I don't think this is a coincidence.

388
00:20:15,520 --> 00:20:17,120
Let's hear what Miss Mingzhu has to say

389
00:20:17,120 --> 00:20:18,680
about Wanqing.

390
00:20:19,560 --> 00:20:20,720
To be honest,

391
00:20:20,960 --> 00:20:24,080
I absolutely don't believe Wanqing would harm my brother.

392
00:20:24,080 --> 00:20:25,600
They've known each other since childhood,

393
00:20:25,600 --> 00:20:27,960
childhood sweethearts and deeply in love.

394
00:20:27,960 --> 00:20:29,720
It's only because of my brother's low status

395
00:20:29,720 --> 00:20:31,880
that he wasn't a match for the eldest daughter of Jiaofang.

396
00:20:31,880 --> 00:20:34,040
Wanqing tried hard to persuade her parents.

397
00:20:34,040 --> 00:20:35,320
They finally agreed.

398
00:20:35,360 --> 00:20:37,360
The wedding was set for next spring.

399
00:20:38,120 --> 00:20:39,760
Although she is a betrothed wife,

400
00:20:39,760 --> 00:20:42,240
she has long become part of our family with my brother.

401
00:20:42,240 --> 00:20:44,170
The two often interact in private.

402
00:20:44,560 --> 00:20:45,760
I really can't figure out

403
00:20:45,760 --> 00:20:48,290
what reason she would have to harm my brother.

404
00:20:48,360 --> 00:20:50,160
In that case,

405
00:20:50,560 --> 00:20:53,200
that Wang Kang had gold thread and gold powder on him

406
00:20:53,200 --> 00:20:54,680
does make sense.

407
00:20:55,720 --> 00:20:56,600
Constable Su.

408
00:20:58,200 --> 00:21:00,520
Didn't you ask me to arrange someone to watch the Jiaofang

409
00:21:00,520 --> 00:21:01,980
and keep an eye on Wanqing?

410
00:21:02,240 --> 00:21:03,970
It turns out she saw a ghost too.

411
00:21:04,280 --> 00:21:05,160
Saw a ghost?

412
00:21:05,200 --> 00:21:06,160
What?

413
00:21:10,760 --> 00:21:14,960
Do you believe there are really ghosts in this world?

414
00:23:50,920 --> 00:23:53,680
In beautiful clothes,

415
00:23:54,040 --> 00:23:56,800
tapping lightly,

416
00:23:57,280 --> 00:24:02,280
the past is gone.

417
00:24:05,440 --> 00:24:08,160
Sister, you sing

418
00:24:08,560 --> 00:24:10,120
so well.

419
00:24:17,120 --> 00:24:18,040
The doctor said

420
00:24:18,120 --> 00:24:19,600
speaking with something in your mouth

421
00:24:19,600 --> 00:24:21,480
can correct your pronunciation.

422
00:24:21,600 --> 00:24:24,040
Can I

423
00:24:24,080 --> 00:24:26,880
go on stage

424
00:24:26,880 --> 00:24:27,920
with you?

425
00:24:27,960 --> 00:24:29,000
You can't.

426
00:24:29,040 --> 00:24:30,360
You can't even speak clearly.

427
00:24:30,360 --> 00:24:32,220
How can we sing on stage together?

428
00:24:45,680 --> 00:24:46,440
Okay.

429
00:24:46,600 --> 00:24:48,200
Our Wanqing is really good.

430
00:24:48,320 --> 00:24:49,760
She dances well, indeed.

431
00:25:03,120 --> 00:25:04,120
Wanqing really

432
00:25:04,320 --> 00:25:05,600
did me proud today.

433
00:25:06,160 --> 00:25:09,360
Today, the Luoyang Magistrate kept praising Wanqing's singing.

434
00:25:09,360 --> 00:25:11,360
Maybe she can go to the Court of Imperial Sacrifices in the future.

435
00:25:11,360 --> 00:25:13,090
Court of Imperial Sacrifices?

436
00:25:13,200 --> 00:25:14,880
It's too hard to get into the Court of Imperial Sacrifices.

437
00:25:14,880 --> 00:25:17,400
If Wanqing could go to the Taile Bureau under it,

438
00:25:17,400 --> 00:25:18,730
that would be great too.

439
00:25:18,920 --> 00:25:19,920
Yes.

440
00:25:20,680 --> 00:25:22,880
Alright, Wanqing, go change your clothes.

441
00:25:22,880 --> 00:25:24,480
We will take you to a banquet.

442
00:25:24,600 --> 00:25:25,840
Go now.

443
00:25:27,880 --> 00:25:29,800
Who do you think this child Wanqing

444
00:25:29,800 --> 00:25:30,720
takes after?

445
00:25:32,960 --> 00:25:34,080
Takes after me.

446
00:25:35,480 --> 00:25:36,840
Yes, takes after you.

447
00:25:38,320 --> 00:25:39,960
Sister! Sister!

448
00:25:42,400 --> 00:25:44,680
Nianyao, did you see Wanrou?

449
00:25:44,800 --> 00:25:46,600
She said she was going to the river.

450
00:25:46,600 --> 00:25:48,400
I don't know what she wants to do.

451
00:25:51,240 --> 00:25:52,800
Wanqing! Wanqing!

452
00:25:53,600 --> 00:25:55,160
Wanrou! Wanrou!

453
00:25:55,600 --> 00:25:59,440
Where could they have run off to? Where do you think these two children could go?

454
00:25:59,440 --> 00:26:01,200
Wanrou! Wanrou!

455
00:26:01,720 --> 00:26:02,520
Wanqing!

456
00:26:03,120 --> 00:26:05,080
Wanqing! Wanqing!

457
00:26:05,400 --> 00:26:06,240
Wanrou!

458
00:26:06,280 --> 00:26:08,840
Wanqing! Wanrou!

459
00:26:12,360 --> 00:26:13,280
Wanqing!

460
00:26:14,120 --> 00:26:15,600
I found Wanqing!

461
00:26:17,160 --> 00:26:17,760
Wanqing!

462
00:26:20,360 --> 00:26:20,880
Come.

463
00:26:21,720 --> 00:26:23,240
Let me look at you.

464
00:26:24,680 --> 00:26:25,520
Are you okay?

465
00:26:33,120 --> 00:26:33,960
Qinger!

466
00:26:34,960 --> 00:26:36,040
Where is Rouer?

467
00:26:55,080 --> 00:26:59,440
S-Sister, play with me.

468
00:27:00,680 --> 00:27:03,440
S-Sister,

469
00:27:04,520 --> 00:27:07,320
p-play with me.

470
00:27:08,960 --> 00:27:13,280
Sister, p-play with me.

471
00:27:24,400 --> 00:27:26,400
S-Sister,

472
00:27:27,160 --> 00:27:29,560
p-play with me.

473
00:27:29,680 --> 00:27:30,600
Sister!

474
00:27:30,720 --> 00:27:35,040
Sister, p-play with me.

475
00:28:08,320 --> 00:28:09,560
Wanqing, Wanqing.

476
00:28:10,280 --> 00:28:11,400
Are you okay?

477
00:28:18,640 --> 00:28:20,100
Why is this guy here again?

478
00:28:23,400 --> 00:28:25,680
Someone is helping you solve the case,

479
00:28:25,840 --> 00:28:27,440
and you still get the credit.

480
00:28:27,560 --> 00:28:28,890
What's wrong with that?

481
00:28:31,400 --> 00:28:33,320
I think he has an ulterior motive.

482
00:28:35,080 --> 00:28:36,280
Shut your mouth.

483
00:28:40,400 --> 00:28:42,160
The bronze mirror can really reflect ghosts.

